{"tid":1838954,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［肺炎］唔好去香港迪士尼","createTime":"2020-01-24T08:10:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T17:19:41.000Z","uid":163397,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"be8dec95e6d3cd0d99a6881d979d8bd01952d04a","tid":1838954,"uid":163397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T08:10:39.000Z","msg":"今日入左樂園玩<br />\n聽到著白色衫既人叫佢d手下勤消毒<br />\n<br />\n咁我開始在意啦 見到成個樂園既員工都帶緊口罩<br />\n<br />\n之後比我係員工口中偷聽到 <br />\n佢地口中話武漢黎既人入左去玩 仲要住埋酒店食野 琴日既事黎<br />\n <br />\n所以各位諗一諗 入去玩真係搵命博 要唔要去自己考慮 何況宜家北京果個關閉左 實大把大陸人落去<br />\n香港人共勉之啦"},{"pid":"3199f4fa69ec020106b66a09083a7d2438e0ed8c","tid":1838954,"uid":89958,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T08:24:04.000Z","msg":"已證實！！！<br />\n迪士尼酒店內有武漢逃犯！！據稱向有關員工表示身體不適。但員工上頭表示不用理會！嚴重懷疑刻意隱瞞消息！！！請大家幫忙廣傳🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻"},{"pid":"12f20d06d0c719c6ba6e8dce4a5a833ba6f92042","tid":1838954,"uid":89958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T08:28:59.000Z","msg":"推下先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2f5833714dee1a62c50abd5aeee47ab15a70a99","tid":1838954,"uid":206370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T08:30:13.000Z","msg":"推住先"},{"pid":"6795bc79ac9d65101e19312e036b549d12e73fbb","tid":1838954,"uid":308071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T08:36:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26145a3a5f1413b16d5403d35a97aaa33e733caf","tid":1838954,"uid":14816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T12:55:01.000Z","msg":"圍內通哂天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推"},{"pid":"0f3a9afbfdec3aa0c223004d2aa03833899105e4","tid":1838954,"uid":14816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T12:55:12.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b5a744c166f17c5a1c17772ff2ca0bcedfdf49",